{
  "title": "O sowal no Pangcah/’Amis",
  "titleCh": "阿美族語",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "阿美族語分為五個語別，分別是南勢阿美語、秀姑巒阿美語、海岸阿美語、馬蘭阿美語及恆春阿美語。這樣的劃分方式是早期日本研究學者所做的分法。",
      "ab": "Pakayniay i sowal no Pangcah, lima ko kasasiroma no kasa’etal. O no i ’Amisay, o no Siwkolang, o no Pasawali, o no Falangaw ato no Palidaw. Onini pisilsil to kasasiroma, o nisanga’an no mikadkaday a tamdaw no Ripon itiya ho.",
