    {
      "chinese": "我們阿美族袓先的想法不是這樣的，他們是以部落為主體。太巴塱人的部落在太巴塱，他們所說的語言是太巴塱語。",
      "ab": "O harateng no mato’asay no mita o Pangcah, caay ka matira, o niyaro’ ko litapangan no kasasiroma no sowal. I Tafalongay a tamdaw, i Tafalong ko niyaro’, o no Tafalong ko sowal nangra.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2025/03/25/c382f44f217cd182e0ee1f6c5328770e.mp3",
